<h2>⚠️ GitHub Rate Limit Warning</h2>

<div class="alert-warning">
    <strong>Token "{{token_label}}" is running low on API requests.</strong>
</div>

<div class="stats-grid">
    <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-value">{{remaining}}</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Requests Remaining</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-value">{{reset_at}}</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Reset Time (UTC)</div>
    </div>
</div>

<p>Consider adding more tokens or reducing concurrent operations to avoid service disruption.</p>

<p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;">
    <a href="{{app_url}}/admin/settings" class="button">Manage Tokens</a>
</p>